<Base title="Lost Sheep Detected — Let's Get You Back!">
  <h1>Lost Sheep Detected — Let's Get You Back!</h1>
  <p>We've left the ninety-nine pages behind to search for this one… but it's <em>still</em> lost!</p>
  <p>
    Like the shepherd seeking his wandering sheep, we're determined to bring this page back
    into the fold. Unfortunately, it seems to have strayed a bit too far into the wilderness
    of cyberspace.
  </p>
  <p><strong>Here's what you can do:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Return to the flock</strong> by heading back to the <a href="/">home page</a>.</li>
    <li><strong>Search for what you need</strong> — you might just find it hidden in plain sight.</li>
    <li><strong>Pray for guidance.</strong> Okay, maybe just check the URL first… but prayer never hurts.</li>
  </ul>
  <blockquote class="ui" style="border-left:3px solid var(--gold);background:var(--gold-soft);padding:10px 16px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0;font-style:italic;color:#4a4233;">
    “I went astray like a lost sheep; seek your servant.” — Psalm 118:176 <span style="opacity:.7">(LXX)</span>
  </blockquote>
